# Skills Directory

Executable skills following Anthropic standards.

## Creating Skills

Use skill-creator to scaffold new skills:

```bash
cd agents/skills/skill-creator
npm run init
```

## Skill Structure

```
skill-name/
├── SKILL.md              # Documentation with YAML frontmatter
├── package.json          # Dependencies and scripts
├── scripts/              # Executable implementations
├── references/           # Deep documentation
└── assets/              # Output templates
```

